            <div class="star-entry">★ CLOUD CLUSTER (AWS/AZURE/GCP) — magnitude: primary infrastructure. three-body system. enterprise-grade orbital deployments.</div>
            <div class="star-entry">★ ML NEBULA — composition: ml pipelines, deep learning, reinforcement learning. stanford-calibrated instruments. deeplearning.ai spectral analysis.</div>
            <div class="star-entry">★ GENAI SUPERNOVA — first observed: 2023. expanding rapidly. llms & generative ai. rag systems deployed across enterprise knowledge base.</div>
            <div class="star-entry">★ ENGINEERING CONSTELLATION — python · java · go · rust · sql · bash. six-star formation. visible year-round.</div>
            <div class="star-entry">★ SECURITY BINARY — twin system: ethical hacking + penetration testing. gchq-certified optics. reverse engineering capability.</div>

            <div class="observer-info">OBSERVER: daniele d'agnelli | senior engagement manager, c3 ai</div>

            <div class="obs-footer">
